snippet.title: Dr. Ryan Ridden
snippet.description: I'm a Post Doctoral Research Fellow at the Space Telescope Science Institute studying the frontiers of cosmic cataclysms. With my knowledge and love for science, I break down new discoveries and cool phenomena!
